Oh... Oh, when I was caught masturbating... The man said... in a shady
shop... I came...

I still can't believe that I ended up working in a place like this...
Even now, I can't believe it myself...

And when I thought about suppressing my sexual desire and regaining my
magical power, I realized that I needed male semen...
There has never been a job as convenient as this...

And besides, it seemed much better than allowing the principal to have
my body again.
As if I'm trying to convince myself...

[Manager] I'll say it again, okay? Here, the customer's words are
absolute.

[Manager] Of course, there's no need to do anything beyond the
service...
[Manager] At the very least, you mustn't make a displeased face, okay?

[Manager] Alright, it seems like a customer has arrived. I'm counting
on you.
